column8: Cloudy. Very high (95%) chance of rain, most likely during this afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm later tonight. Light winds becoming east to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the morning then becoming light in the evening.

Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of rain and the risk of a thunderstorm, easing to showers during the morning. The chance of a thunderstorm in the morning. Winds northeasterly 20 to 30 km/h turning northwesterly 35 to 50 km/h in the middle of the day then decreasing to 25 to 40 km/h in the late afternoon.

Partly cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers in the southeast suburbs, medium (60%) chance elsewhere. Winds northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h tending westerly 25 to 35 km/h during the morning then becoming light during the evening.

The chance of morning fog in the outer eastern suburbs. Partly cloudy day. Medium (50%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. Winds north to northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h tending northwest to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
The chance of morning fog in the outer eastern suburbs. Partly cloudy day. Medium (40%) chance of showers. Light winds becoming south to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day.
Partly cloudy. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. Light winds becoming southeast to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the day.
Mostly sunny. Light winds becoming southeast to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day.
